001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonCreator;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
005import org.bitcoinj.base.Coin;
006import org.bitcoinj.base.Sha256Hash;
007
008import java.util.Map;
009
010/**
011 * Result of `gettxout`
012 */
013public class TxOutInfo {
014    private final Sha256Hash bestblock;
015    private final int        confirmations;
016    private final Coin       value;
017    private final Map        scriptPubKey;
018    private final int        version;
019    private final boolean    coinbase;
020
021    @JsonCreator
022    public TxOutInfo(@JsonProperty("bestblock")     Sha256Hash  bestblock,
023                     @JsonProperty("confirmations") int         confirmations,
024                     @JsonProperty("value")         Coin        value,
025                     @JsonProperty("scriptPubKey")  Map         scriptPubKey,
026                     @JsonProperty("version")       int         version,
027                     @JsonProperty("coinbase")      boolean     coinbase) {
028        this.bestblock = bestblock;
029        this.confirmations = confirmations;
030        this.value = value;
031        this.scriptPubKey = scriptPubKey;
032        this.version = version;
033        this.coinbase = coinbase;
034    }
035
036    public Sha256Hash getBestblock() {
037        return bestblock;
038    }
039
040    public int getConfirmations() {
041        return confirmations;
042    }
043
044    public Coin getValue() {
045        return value;
046    }
047
048    public Map getScriptPubKey() {
049        return scriptPubKey;
050    }
051
052    public int getVersion() {
053        return version;
054    }
055
056    public boolean isCoinbase() {
057        return coinbase;
058    }
059}
